{"case_id": "challenge-coding-001", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "parser", "state"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "2ca132befd6923601a17f24e5efb427ea787e3ae63ae265dd45f0c700cd895d6", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:48:36.927177+00:00", "latency_ms": 16737, "output": " ```python\ndef solve(lines: list[str]) -> dict:\n    result = {}\n    current = None\n    for line in lines:\n        s = line.strip()\n        if not s or s.startswith('#'):\n            continue\n        if s.startswith('[') and s.endswith(']'):\n            current = s[1:-1].strip()\n            result.setdefault(current, {})\n            continue\n        if '=' in s and current is not None:\n            key, value = s.split('=', 1)\n            result[current][key.strip()] = value.strip()\n    return result\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 111, "completion_tokens": 360, "total_tokens": 471, "cost": 0.00154545, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00154545, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.00010545, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00144}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 295, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585319-o9pKx0sYOBonDKnTuY5X", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-002", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "ledger", "state"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "3d2d5a46a600444476b5ddfd04634035ff394bcb76fcd230d785597c9cf295ae", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:48:53.697727+00:00", "latency_ms": 23849, "output": "```python\ndef solve(events: list[str]) -> int:\n    balance = 0\n    txs = {}\n    for ev in events:\n        parts = ev.split()\n        if len(parts) == 3:\n            tid, typ, amt = parts[0], parts[1], int(parts[2])\n            if tid in txs:\n                continue\n            if typ == \"credit\":\n                balance += amt\n                txs[tid] = (\"credit\", amt, True)\n            elif typ == \"debit\":\n                balance -= amt\n                txs[tid] = (\"debit\", amt, True)\n        elif len(parts) == 2 and parts[0] == \"rev\":\n            tid = parts[1]\n            tx = txs.get(tid)\n            if tx and tx[2]:\n                typ, amt, _ = tx\n                if typ == \"credit\":\n                    balance -= amt\n                else:\n                    balance += amt\n                txs[tid] = (typ, amt, False)\n    return balance\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 112, "completion_tokens": 714, "total_tokens": 826, "cost": 0.00287728, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 112, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00287728, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 2.128e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.002856}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 572, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585335-TkGqf30jJr3GVvjgjdY3", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-003", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "topological-sort"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "413c5b602b0fd1ae1e9c3a49b09ecf03c61769fce4b34dbd96b5d8c6a2c68f90", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:49:17.592619+00:00", "latency_ms": 37479, "output": "```python\ndef solve(deps: dict[str, list[str]]) -> list[list[str]]:\n    nodes = set(deps)\n    for prereqs in deps.values():\n        nodes.update(prereqs)\n\n    indeg = {n: 0 for n in nodes}\n    adj = {n: [] for n in nodes}\n\n    for task, prereqs in deps.items():\n        seen = set()\n        for p in prereqs:\n            if p not in seen:\n                seen.add(p)\n                indeg[task] += 1\n                adj[p].append(task)\n\n    remaining = set(nodes)\n    result = []\n\n    while remaining:\n        layer = sorted(n for n in remaining if indeg[n] == 0)\n        if not layer:\n            return []\n        result.append(layer)\n        for n in layer:\n            remaining.remove(n)\n            for nb in adj[n]:\n                indeg[nb] -= 1\n\n    return result\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 102, "completion_tokens": 731, "total_tokens": 833, "cost": 0.0030209, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0030209, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 9.69e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.002924}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 636, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585359-JekodmWkFRhyEI87LrTe", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-004", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "lru"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "840e7b4d0c404f3d7b34ebc9931e87612608d6339755d5f1066fda55bd957375", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:49:55.107660+00:00", "latency_ms": 25401, "output": "```python\nfrom collections import OrderedDict\n\ndef solve(capacity: int, ops: list[str]) -> list[int]:\n    cache: OrderedDict[int, int] = OrderedDict()\n    res: list[int] = []\n    if capacity == 0:\n        for op in ops:\n            if op.startswith(\"get\"):\n                res.append(-1)\n        return res\n    for op in ops:\n        parts = op.split()\n        if parts[0] == \"put\":\n            key = int(parts[1])\n            value = int(parts[2])\n            if key in cache:\n                cache.move_to_end(key)\n            else:\n                if len(cache) == capacity:\n                    cache.popitem(last=False)\n                cache[key] = value\n        else:\n            key = int(parts[1])\n            if key in cache:\n                cache.move_to_end(key)\n                res.append(cache[key])\n            else:\n                res.append(-1)\n    return res\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 117, "completion_tokens": 461, "total_tokens": 578, "cost": 0.00195515, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00195515, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.00011115, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.001844}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 281, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585397-RUlBncTK0fauimaNnsKW", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": false, "score": 0.0, "details": {"returncode": 1, "stdout": "", "stderr": "Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/var/folders/x_/4cht1kfj1_j31gdv5w01sgmw0000gn/T/dracobench-code-4bdxyr0s/test_solution.py\", line 4, in <module>\n    assert solution.solve(2, ops) == [1, -1, 1, 3]\n           ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/private/var/folders/x_/4cht1kfj1_j31gdv5w01sgmw0000gn/T/dracobench-code-4bdxyr0s/solution.py\", line 14, in solve\n    key = int(parts[1])\n          ^^^^^^^^^^^^^\nValueError: invalid literal for int() with base 10: 'a'\n"}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-005", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "json", "copy"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "8dc22406b418d74ea74b50692fe086d4f80748258269dc93f82290e6c344b5a3", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:50:20.551291+00:00", "latency_ms": 29902, "output": "```python\ndef solve(base: dict, patch: dict) -> dict:\n    result = dict(base)\n    for key, value in patch.items():\n        if value is None:\n            result.pop(key, None)\n        elif isinstance(value, dict) and isinstance(result.get(key), dict):\n            result[key] = solve(result[key], value)\n        else:\n            result[key] = value\n    return result\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 93, "completion_tokens": 598, "total_tokens": 691, "cost": 0.00248035, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00248035, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 8.835e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.002392}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 611, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585422-oAtVnzXthVyvRg2NjwSM", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-006", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "regex", "duration"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "ce87366a2f6f080a35c0fdd0872b6a8304a8233e0c5c9361c19fec614c0d1fcb", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:50:50.481076+00:00", "latency_ms": 7946, "output": " ```python\nimport re\n\ndef solve(text: str) -> int:\n    units = {\"ms\": 1, \"s\": 1000, \"m\": 60000, \"h\": 3600000, \"d\": 86400000}\n    total = 0\n    for m in re.finditer(r'(-?\\d+)\\s*(ms|m|s|h|d)', text):\n        total += int(m.group(1)) * units[m.group(2)]\n    return total\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 93, "completion_tokens": 350, "total_tokens": 443, "cost": 0.00129475, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00129475, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 6.975e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.001225}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 240, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585452-pF8xbAOfI9MRQeJN3CIG", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-007", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "parser", "quotes"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "2f2e8f01533244c8104f74b3f9c9bc261154f2ff4c46c03a031258f6a5706f9f", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:50:58.466431+00:00", "latency_ms": 24001, "output": "```python\ndef solve(s: str) -> bool:\n    stack = []\n    quote = None\n    i = 0\n    n = len(s)\n    while i < n:\n        c = s[i]\n        if c == '\\\\' and i + 1 < n and s[i + 1] in (\"'\", '\"'):\n            i += 2\n            continue\n        if c in (\"'\", '\"'):\n            if quote is None:\n                quote = c\n            elif quote == c:\n                quote = None\n            i += 1\n            continue\n        if quote is None:\n            if c in '([{':\n                stack.append(c)\n            elif c in ')]}':\n                if not stack:\n                    return False\n                top = stack.pop()\n                if (top == '(' and c != ')') or (top == '[' and c != ']') or (top == '{' and c != '}'):\n                    return False\n        i += 1\n    return not stack\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 90, "completion_tokens": 1501, "total_tokens": 1591, "cost": 0.0060895, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0060895, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 8.55e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.006004}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 1483, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585460-oprpPgsGU1VAeHi2ugUa", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-008", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "dedupe", "sorting"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "2a9a2d40a756627e38d28a8ac6afc98311acbafa718d7b3aaaecbedb9f020179", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:51:22.509532+00:00", "latency_ms": 23546, "output": "```python\ndef solve(rows: list[dict]) -> list[dict]:\n    best = {}\n    for i, row in enumerate(rows):\n        user = row['user']\n        key = (row['ts'], i)\n        if user not in best or key >= best[user][0]:\n            best[user] = (key, row)\n    return [row for _, row in sorted(best.items())]\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 100, "completion_tokens": 344, "total_tokens": 444, "cost": 0.001471, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.001471, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 9.5e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.001376}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 269, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585484-E2MQ6CtbzExwCj8wcUon", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": false, "score": 0.0, "details": {"returncode": 1, "stdout": "", "stderr": "Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/var/folders/x_/4cht1kfj1_j31gdv5w01sgmw0000gn/T/dracobench-code-iqjvo6oo/test_solution.py\", line 4, in <module>\n    assert solution.solve(rows) == [{'user':'a','ts':2,'value':'x'}, {'user':'b','ts':3,'value':'new'}]\nAssertionError\n"}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-debugging-001", "suite": "debugging", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "iterator-default", "debugging"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "7b02a617eebe49b179cee84c9b8347c6bebe382f42a2b199d92b3aa9ed844102", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:51:46.079444+00:00", "latency_ms": 40229, "output": "根因：Python 的默认参数在函数定义时只计算一次，`iter([1, 2, 3])` 创建的是一个**迭代器对象**，会被所有调用共享。第一次 `sum(items)` 会把它耗尽，之后再次调用时用的已经是空迭代器，所以结果为 0。\n\n最小修复：把默认值改为不可变的 `None`，在函数内部再创建迭代器。\n\n```python\ndef summarize(items=None):\n    if items is None:\n        items = iter([1, 2, 3])\n    return sum(items)\n```\n\nFIX: def summarize(items=None):", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 99, "completion_tokens": 743, "total_tokens": 842, "cost": 0.00306605, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00306605, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 9.405e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.002972}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 778, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585508-Gh6Z1Lo227MfXOvIS3ad", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"pattern": "FIX:\\s*`?\\s*def\\s+summarize\\(items=None\\)\\s*:"}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-debugging-002", "suite": "debugging", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "defaultdict", "debugging"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "fc1eb426cf811456432a61a306862f8bf804417edb8c8fca6dd3b86c1f9a9940", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:52:26.311117+00:00", "latency_ms": 4687, "output": " 根因：`defaultdict` 的工厂函数 `lambda: shared` 每次都返回**同一个**字典对象，因此所有用户共享同一份 `{'seen': []}`，导致计数互相影响。\n\n最小修复：让工厂函数每次返回一个新的独立字典。\n\nFIX: `counts = defaultdict(lambda: {'seen': []})`", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 122, "completion_tokens": 291, "total_tokens": 413, "cost": 0.0012799, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0012799, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001159, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.001164}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 279, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585548-0dQRzRejrBkANqYwBkh8", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"pattern": "FIX:\\s*`?\\s*counts\\s*=\\s*defaultdict\\(lambda\\s*:\\s*\\{'seen'\\s*:\\s*\\[\\]\\}\\)\\s*`?"}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-debugging-003", "suite": "debugging", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "off-by-one", "debugging"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 4096, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "c6fe209d60968a3b2d253a065c8ce8255865f73575665a685d957cb52ce82011", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:52:31.000317+00:00", "latency_ms": 4836, "output": " bug：`range` 的结束值写成了 `len(items) - page_size`，导致最后一页（长度不足 `page_size` 时）不会被遍历到。\n\n最小修复：把结束值改为 `len(items)`，切片 `items[start:start + page_size]` 会自动处理最后一页。\n\nFIX: for start in range(0, len(items), page_size):", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 121, "completion_tokens": 323, "total_tokens": 444, "cost": 0.00120237, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 32, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00120237, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 7.187e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.0011305}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 244, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781585553-NipOxMg0UKf8ttUPF9iA", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"pattern": "FIX:\\s*`?\\s*for\\s+start\\s+in\\s+range\\(0,\\s*len\\(items\\),\\s*page_size\\)\\s*:"}}, "error": null}
